Class Annotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • cw_1201592.Annotation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Annotation>

    public class Annotation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Annotation>
    Stores data for a tagging behavior. Instances of this class store:
    • the tag of an annotation, as an ADT Tag and
    • an integer value for the count of the annotation.
    Each of these has a getter and setter method.
    Author:
    Boqing Liu
